Feature	Support
Multimodal (text + images)	✅
Video input	✅ (via unified structure)
Audio input	✅ (via unified structure)
PDF input	✅ (via unified structure)
Streaming	✅
Function Calling	✅
Google Search Grounding	✅
Structured Output (JSON Schema)	✅
Reasoning tokens	✅ (include_thoughts, reasoning_effort)
Usage Flow
Prepare messages: Create an array of messages with text and/or media parts

Optional features: Add tools, response_format, stream, or reasoning parameters as needed

Send request: POST to the endpoint with your API key

Handle response: Parse the JSON response or process SSE events if streaming

Check usage: Monitor token usage for cost management

